Basic Assumtions
================
     1.  While adding an entry in 'samAsa-new.txt'  a phrase without any punctuations should be entered.
     2.  For the time being  a phrase with or without comma has the same meaning.
              Ex:  if so --> yaxi_EsA_hE_wo  is same as  If so , --> yaxi_EsA_ho_wo
